  <entry>
    <title>对递归的理解</title>
    <url>/2021/05/28/%E5%AF%B9%E9%80%92%E5%BD%92%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>递归</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="递归"><a href="#递归" class="headerlink" title="递归"></a>递归</h2><p>简单地说，<strong>方法自己调用自己</strong>，这种现象就叫递归。递归和循环很像，循环可以改写成递归，但递归却不一定可以改写成循环。</p>
<p>如果是简单循环当然用循环方便些，但在某些情况下，递归比循环要简洁方便很多。</p>
<p>我们先从简单的例子说起，比如，我们要进行求和1~10，用for循环时，是这样的:</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">int</span> sum = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt;= <span class="number">10</span>; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    	sum += i;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;sum = &quot;</span> + sum);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>若是用递归，则是这样的:</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;sum = &quot;</span>+ sum(<span class="number">10</span>));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">sum</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> n)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(n == <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> sum(n - <span class="number">1</span>) + n;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这样，递归好像不比循环方便，但在别的应用中就不一样了。</p>
<h3 id="在C语言中的应用"><a href="#在C语言中的应用" class="headerlink" title="在C语言中的应用"></a>在C语言中的应用</h3><p>例如，我最近在写c语言实验中遇到这样一个题:</p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/05/30/sf5W4JnC2rg8uRz.png" alt="8.png"></p>
<p>在写的过程中，我尝试用循环写，但实话说，越写越懵，最后也没能运行成功。</p>
<p>于是，我问了一个大佬，这才想到用递归方法 :</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Try</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> i)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> like[<span class="number">5</span>][<span class="number">5</span>] = &#123;&#123;<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">0</span>&#125;, &#123;<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>&#125;, &#123;<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>&#125;, &#123;<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">0</span>&#125;, &#123;<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>&#125;&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> book[<span class="number">5</span>] = &#123;<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>&#125;;<span class="comment">//book[i]代表第几个人拿走了第i+1本书.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> n = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Try</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> i)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> j, k;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(j = <span class="number">0</span>; j &lt; <span class="number">5</span>; j++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(like[i][j] == <span class="number">1</span> &amp;&amp; book[j] == <span class="number">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            book[j] = i + <span class="number">1</span>; <span class="comment">//将第j+1本书分给第i+1个人</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(i == <span class="number">4</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                n++;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;第%d种分配方案为:\n&quot;</span>,n);</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">for</span>(k = <span class="number">0</span>; k &lt; <span class="number">5</span>; k++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;第%d本书分给%c\n&quot;</span>, k + <span class="number">1</span>, book[k] + <span class="string">&#x27;A&#x27;</span> - <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                Try(i + <span class="number">1</span>); <span class="comment">//如果还有人没分到书则递归给下一个人分书</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            book[j] = <span class="number">0</span>; <span class="comment">//回溯重新将第j本书恢复成未选中状态</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    Try(i);    </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这样看是不是很清晰地就解决了问题。</p>
<h3 id="在Java中的应用"><a href="#在Java中的应用" class="headerlink" title="在Java中的应用"></a>在Java中的应用</h3><h4 id="一、冒泡排序"><a href="#一、冒泡排序" class="headerlink" title="一、冒泡排序"></a>一、冒泡排序</h4><p>对一数组进行由大到小排序:</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span>[] arrays = &#123;<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">29</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">6</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    bubbleSort(arrays, <span class="number">0</span>, arrays.length - <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;排序后为:&quot;</span> + arrays);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">bubbleSort</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span>[] arrays, <span class="keyword">int</span> L, <span class="keyword">int</span> R)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> temp;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(L != R)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i = L; i &lt; R; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(arrays[i] &lt; arrays[i+<span class="number">1</span>])&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                temp = arrays[i];</span><br><span class="line">                arrays[i] = arrays[i + <span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">                arrays[i + <span class="number">1</span>] = temp;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;   <span class="comment">//第一趟排序将最小值放在数组最后面...</span></span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">        bubbleSort(arrays, L, R - <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/05/30/O6M1v2KaqBEYjbz.jpg" alt="IMG_0184.PNG"></p>
<p>冒泡排序的具体过程我就不多讲了。</p>
<h4 id="二、斐波那契数"><a href="#二、斐波那契数" class="headerlink" title="二、斐波那契数"></a>二、斐波那契数</h4><p>这是我在leetcode上找到的一道题，让我们来看一下这道题，很明显，用递归会更加方便。</p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/05/30/hlgYDctfILqdvTx.png" alt="f.png"></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">fib</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> n)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> Fib;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(n == <span class="number">1</span> || n == <span class="number">2</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Fib = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>(n == <span class="number">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Fib = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Fib = fib(n - <span class="number">1</span>) + fib(n - <span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> Fib;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h3 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h3><p>使用递归对<strong>前提</strong>是:</p>
<ul>
<li>知道终止递归的条件</li>
<li>递归的表达式（即其规律）    </li>
</ul>
<p>总之，递归的本质就是<strong>方法自己调用自己，只是参数在改变</strong>。</p>
]]></content>
  </entry>
